Description: ================
        inmagik-drf-auth
        ================
        
        Additional views and helpers that we always use with django rest framework
        
        
        Quick start
        -----------
        
        1. Add "inmagik_drf_auth" to your INSTALLED_APPS setting like this::
        
            INSTALLED_APPS = (
                ...
                'inmagik_drf_auth',
            )
        
        
